Feature: View comments from other customers

    As a customer I want to see the evaluation comments of clients who have purchased the service to be able to have confidence in hiring the company and, thus, remodel my house.

    Scenario: The customer views the comments of other customers
    Given the user is in the “Presentation of projects Before and After” section
    When he scroll to the “Comments” section.
    Then the customer can view the recommendations or ratings made by customers.